OL,3,CPrisoner charged with murder of inmate
OL,5,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,6,Fafter the death of a fellow inmate in
OL,7,Fprison, police have said.
OL,9,FTony Joynes, 47, was found dead in his
OL,10,Fcell at HMP Garth near Leyland,
OL,11,FLancashire, on 13 July.
OL,13,FAn investigation was launched by
OL,14,Fpolice and a prisoner aged in his 30s
OL,15,Fwas arrested at the Category B jail
OL,16,Flater that month on suspicion of
OL,17,Fmurder.
