OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774605947
OL,3,CPrisoner charged with murder of inmate
OL,5,FOn Thursday, Lancashire Constabulary
OL,6,Fsaid in a statement: "Following
OL,7,Fconsultation with the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service, we have charged
OL,9,FShaun Newton, 35, with the murder of
OL,10,FMr Joynes.
OL,12,F"Newton, who remains in the custody of
OL,13,Fthe Prison Service, will appear before
OL,14,FPreston Magistrates' Court today."
OL,16,FJoynes was jailed for 15 years in 2020
OL,17,Fafter he carried out an axe and knife
OL,18,Fattack on a couple in their home in
OL,19,FWorkington, Cumbria.
